expression = re.compile(rfc._DOMAIN_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['127.1.1', '127.a.1.1',
    '2001:0dg8:0000:0000:0000:ff00:0042:8329', '7', '-', 'a.-aa', 'a.7aa',
    'a-', 'a.', '.a', '']
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad domain '{l}' matched regex".format(l=bad_example))
